~B~2-- ~0Overview ~2--~B

The object is to find, capture, and hold between 3 and 6 flags at strategic points on the map.
A team can win one of 2 ways, either by holding all flags for 20 seconds OR by having the most 
flags at the end of the game timer. Each team has up to 40 players.

(No Man's Land is the exception; NML the only objective is to shoot the enemy. In Skirmish at 
Outpost Delta, When you die, you will respawn near a flag that your team owns. There is a limit 
to it: The more ppl near the flag in question, the less likely anyone will respawn there. If you
cant be placed, you will respawn at base.)

Use the keywords ?score or ?flags at game start to keep track of flags.


