~B~2-- ~0Voice Macros ~2--~B

Voice Macros are EFFECTIVE. Dont be afraid to use them. Remember to use %coord to tell your map 
coordinates!

Voice Macro Sounds
Bong #    Says:
22	    Acknowledged
23	    Affirmative
24	    Attacking
25	    Defending
26	    Enemy Sighted
27	    Request Summon
28        Under Attack

You can use these macros like this:
//your message here %<bong number>
For Example: //I am under attack! %28


